com.adriangarcia.cnop

Class QuadraticallyConstrainedQuadraticProgram

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.adriangarcia.metaheuristics.tsmbfoa.Problem
      • com.adriangarcia.cnop.QuadraticallyConstrainedQuadraticProgram

  • public class QuadraticallyConstrainedQuadraticProgram
extends Problem
    QuadraticallyConstrainedQuadraticProgram class that creates a test CNOP. This CNOP has as objective function:

    Minimize: x1^4 - 14 * x1^2 + 24 * x1 - x2^2
    Subject to: -x1 + x2 - 8 <= 0 <= 0
    x2 - x1^2 - 2 * x1 + 2 <= 0
    where: (-8,10),(0,10)
    This class inherits the mechanisms of the Problem class.
    Version:
    1.0
